text: Hello <@U03TLB8D996> here are some questions that can be useful for you:

- in what technology, this website has been built?
- Does that form has a captcha?
- How information is passing between platforms via API and which platforms they are using?
- Any plugins or apps included?
And in this url you can find some information about  HubSpot Developers: <https://legacydocs.HubSpot.com/docs/methods/forms/submit_form>

I know this is really old, but I found this and tried using it today. Found initially that it did not work, but it was because the code has "groupID" but needs to be "groupId" (with a lowercase d). Changing that made it work for me. Posting here for reference of anyone else that takes this for a spin. Thanks for sharing it!

If you did that today, it was be inexcusable. But two years ago... all good! haha

Still, I was looking for an example of this exact thing and this was helpful!
